{"tid":2122905,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"凍薪、馳援 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-07-24T09:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T09:22:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"695aa4aee53fcb1a0bb5d1a678265b627d05e34a","tid":2122905,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200724/20962009/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200724%2F20962009%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6BBMzzOW1qmypsfK5hxWA9U%3D&h=7a4219e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200724%2F20962009%2F&h=79685f99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200724/20962009/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n凍薪、馳援 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200724/large/1595486900_f7f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200724%2Flarge%2F1595486900_f7f5.jpg&h=f8f4fd7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去幾個月，香港抗疫戰最勞苦功高的是誰？相信首推本港醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n自從武漢爆發武漢肺炎以來，各國先後封關，香港政府到這刻為止，仍未真正封關，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n想像一下如果你是一個前線醫護人員，面對傳染性極強的新型病毒，冒着被感染的風險救治病人，同時強忍着跟家人隔離的痛苦，你希望得到甚麼？最低限度是政府的尊重和理解。誰能想像，不肯封關、持續引入病毒的政府，偏偏對醫護人員冷酷無情。甚至打算引入中國醫生，是「馳援」還是欲取代香港醫護人員？我不打算猜測，相信用不了太久，時間會告訴我們答案是甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n香港的醫護人員，。。。。。。。。。。、趕盡殺絕，能不叫人心寒？<br />\n<br />\n法律界、教育界、醫療界，還有公務員隊伍&hellip;&hellip;一個一個專業隊伍被取代，變得面目全非，香港還剩下甚麼？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"}]}